ADDTEAM A
ADDTEAM B
ADDTEAM C
START DURATION 100 PROBLEM 5
SUBMIT A BY A WITH Wrong_Answer AT 10
SUBMIT A BY A WITH Wrong_Answer AT 15
SUBMIT A BY A WITH Accepted AT 20
SUBMIT B BY B WITH Accepted AT 25
SUBMIT C BY C WITH Accepted AT 30
FLUSH
QUERY_SUBMISSION A WHERE PROBLEM=A AND STATUS=Accepted
QUERY_SUBMISSION B WHERE PROBLEM=ALL AND STATUS=ALL
QUERY_SUBMISSION C WHERE PROBLEM=C AND STATUS=Wrong_Answer
END